QuestData.Title: Sanctum of Domination - Damned If You Don't
QuestData.Description:
I feel Kel'Thuzad's presence in these halls. Claim shards from his phylactery and I'll be able to open a new pathway into his chambers.
Four shards should be enough. We wouldn't want him coming back again would we?
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 4 Phylactery Shards from Kel'Thuzad within the Sanctum of Domination on Mythic Difficulty.
